Entries.default: "Oh. Oh, no. No, thank you. No."
"Of course this place has a spider wing."
"Careful with your flames. It is a very long way down."
"What say we be tossing a few cinder bombs in and call it a day, aye?"
"Lord of light, how big's a spider gotta be to make this?"
"Try not to step on anything. Some of us enjoy having blood."
"A Vithrack colony wouldn't have spread this far unless it was put to good use."
"What is this place? There were perfectly good cages below!"
